{"tid":1796492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2019聖誕精選集","createTime":"2019-12-24T15:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T17:54:46.000Z","uid":73293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89b5f51ca10f5fff397d48315fd32464d22b1e60","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"每年香港聖誕氣氛濃厚<br />\n除了元旦會倒數慶新年，<br />\n連平安夜也會倒數慶聖誕<br />\n很可惜今年警察為了反洋節<br />\n決定以催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、鮮血來洗滌2019的聖誕節。<br />\n不知道10年後或100年後這post會否被消息<br />\n只想提醒未來的香港人<br />\n請不要忘記黑警在這半年如何暴力對待市民。<br />\n<br />\n2019年12月24日 朗豪坊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqwvD8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqwvD8Z.jpg&h=688ef0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wH4Umnk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwH4Umnk.jpg&h=1e6dfa9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnhnvfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnhnvfF.jpg&h=43b71263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tk2Zxt0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTk2Zxt0.jpg&h=2d3cbc50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpKUmnk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpKUmnk.jpg&h=8e391674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以胡椒水攻擊記者"},{"pid":"d6ff346c249a2535c04bc6a966aa2ecb351c1aa2","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PinOqPt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPinOqPt.jpg&h=3cc3cd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7Rjxuu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7Rjxuu.jpg&h=cb4d5ba8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14595176e30dff35ed9e57d6044c82046d6308d7","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl