r />\n甚至以催淚煙阻止市民參與報佳音。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMDNGrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMDNGrH.jpg&h=4e8e19a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F432vj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF432vj3.jpg&h=01ec3374&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sfAwoE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsfAwoE4.jpg&h=a417df18&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bxaz5Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxaz5Tp.jpg&h=b7d0caeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yhtuaj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhtuaj5.jpg&h=1a6ff461&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2fbe0d251592f7a38ad4e19cd80d8ab9809b1bc","tid":1796492,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警暴不止，反抗不息</span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote>面具1個10hkd，<br />\n假設黃店全部以10hkd購入，<br />\n然後全部以10HKD 賣出，<br />\n同時提供黃店（所有食肆／商舖）優惠話，<br />\n食肆：付費時出示面具可以每人頭面具數，每人減5HKD<br />\n商舖：付費滿50HKD出示面具可全單減5HKD，<br />\n你話有冇得諗？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q973eDC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq973eDC.png&h=1d34a395&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n[商業奇才]惠顧滿50HKD出示V煞面具全單減5HKD, 有無得諗？<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1796489/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1796489/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e0e8f75b78142ba8d35dc5fd7b359ed3fa1d6194","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZXR78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZXR78c.jpg&h=a5e3abc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpcOqUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpcOqUT.jpg&h=969aa144&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"204e72bc5ea1003b4a5934f694f49ca0bb5bc7d1","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"12月24日 朗豪坊商場內<br />\n黑警以警棍不斷嘔打市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC8U5U6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC8U5U6.jpg&h=8650bdb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpMrW2h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpMrW2h.jpg&h=4f75f1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦以胡椒噴霧不斷噴向記者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9Pw78U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9Pw78U.jpg&h=482f8cd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abe909fd37876024fdaf5aa1b36280f6a0ee92af","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"今年的平安夜<br />\n是多麼的不平安<br />\n是否黑警想以催淚彈呼喚耶穌下來？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRLgzPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRLgzPV.jpg&h=64cc34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水炮車2號在尖沙咀 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tfouaof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfouaof.jpg&h=bbc77012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"113d773415635f185a5abbd8fa331708389c6c5f","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"迷霧漫漫的The One<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYiaEg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYiaEg1.jpg&h=4cf2cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餐廳內的職員與食客也受影響<br />\n真正想攪炒的其實是黑警和林鄭<br />\n沒有他們的加持<br />\n如何能令商店馬上關門？<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3CVQoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3CVQoG.jpg&h=c5ae5841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb015c078eaefab637182aeeb83c1e79f4bdb20a","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"踏入聖誕節<br />\n以往也是倒數聲和歡呼聲<br />\n今年卻是無數開槍聲<br />\n以及市民恐慌和痛苦的叫聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HXOqYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HXOqYj.jpg&h=9c11f352&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黑警再一次射記者眼"},{"pid":"72c8a1894c5af0e3b83a40e75ad1d8adb2bcaea7","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:32:59.000Z","msg":"2019平安夜之沙田區<br />\n這些人不是示威者，而是便衣黑警<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWSF1yo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWSF1yo.jpg&h=a42e8057&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZimLZ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZimLZ3.jpg&h=4b2476ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UWWzTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UWWzTp.jpg&h=a27785a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p20gzTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp20gzTp.jpg&h=d7b77efd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n在沙田拘捕市民期間，<br />\n被捕人士留下小量血<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dKC6W7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdKC6W7f.jpg&h=1ab5e7ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9a09fd4b6a43abf12e1965f1b37a9adc941515c","tid":1796492,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀海港城<br />\n請問平安夜去海旁消費<br />\n是犯了什麼法？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpGvEkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpGvEkN.jpg&h=65526c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yo9JeT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYo9JeT7.jpg&h=df7f47ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LmC3Nt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LmC3Nt.jpg&